00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:22,640
 Cool.

229
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,720
 (audience laughing)

230
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,800
 Anyways, 1 Timothy 2.

231
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:29,360
 If you have time, go back home and read that passage.

232
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:32,800
 Paul is actually doing something very funny to us.

