00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:22,560
 Well, unspoken rule.

250
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:26,760
 I remember one time we were still in college.

251
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:30,320
 We were going with some friends to Los Angeles.

252
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:32,600
 So we were driving down from Northern California.

253
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:35,480
 I was in Sacramento at that point.

254
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:39,200
 And then we drove down to Los Angeles for vacation.

255
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:42,240
 So some of our friends, we went to Hollywood,

256
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,080
 we went to

257
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,720
 Universal Studio and all those stuff, right?

258
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,880
 The fun stuff.

259
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:51,480
 So on Sunday, we found a church.

