00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:22,680
 I live by faith in the Son of God.

537
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:27,620
 And He loved me and gave Himself for me.

538
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:33,120
 This is no longer something out there,

539
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:36,640
 some objective fact or something that happened

540
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:39,280
 in the world, in time and space.

541
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:41,080
 Yes, that's true, historical fact,

542
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:43,680
 and Pontius Pilate, Jesus, the real guy,

543
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:45,760
 and all that stuff, empty tomb.

544
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:48,760
 It becomes a subjective experience.

545
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:52,080
 It becomes your own personal experience.

546
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:57,920
 Christianity, biblical faith, it's all about relationship.

547
00:29:57,920 --> 00:30:01,640
 It is your relationship with Christ.

548
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:04,040
 But please understand, this sort of relationship

549
00:30:04,040 --> 00:30:06,680
 is not just, "Oh, you know, patting my back,

550
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,420
 "and you'll be okay."

551
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:12,800
 It's a radical transformation, how we see the world,

552
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:14,960
 and how we see ourselves.

553
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:17,280
 Well, I want to recite the Apostles' Creed together,

554
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:19,700
 and then we'll pray together.

555
00:30:19,700 --> 00:30:22,160
 That's all we recite together.

556
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,320
 You all stand.

557
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:29,480
 Apostles' Creed.

558
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,600
 Let's recite together.

559
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:33,720
 I believe in God, the God Almighty,

560
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:35,560
 creator of heaven and earth.

561
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:39,120
 I believe in Jesus Christ, His only Son, our Lord.

562
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:42,360
 He was conceived by the power of the Holy Spirit,

563
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,360
 and born of the Virgin Mary.

564
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:46,480
 He suffered under Pontius Pilate,

565
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:49,440
 was crucified, died, and was buried.

566
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,240
 He descended to the dead.

567
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,160
 On the third day, He rose again.

568
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,960
 He ascended into heaven,

569
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:57,920
 and is now seated at the right hand of the Father.

570
00:30:57,920 --> 00:31:00,640
 He will come again to judge the living and the dead.

571
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:04,280
 I believe in the Holy Spirit, the holy universal church,

572
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:08,120
 the communion of saints, the covenants of sin.

573
00:31:08,120 --> 00:31:13,320
 Let's all pray.

574
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:17,600
 Father, I give you thanks for breaking into our reality,

575
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:19,720
 breaking into our world,

576
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:22,140
 to tell us that you are real,

577
00:31:22,140 --> 00:31:27,240
 to tell us that you have done something mighty,

578
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:30,280
 something that is beyond our explanation

579
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:32,800
 in real time and real space.

580
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:35,760
 In history, you have come,

581
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:38,800
 and you die on the cross for our sins,

582
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:40,400
 and you rose from the dead

583
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:43,760
 to give us new hope and eternal life.

584
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:48,440
 Father, this new reality, may you help us to be reminded

585
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:50,020
 and to stand on it,

586
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:55,560
 to base our whole life on this foundation,

587
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:59,000
 knowing that your kingdom is eternal,

588
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,480
 and your kingdom will come.

589
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:04,560
 And we pray that your kingdom will come into our lives,

590
00:32:04,560 --> 00:32:06,160
 change us gradually,

591
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:11,760
 radically transform us into the image of your Son.

592
00:32:11,760 --> 00:32:14,240
 And thank you for the relationship that we have

593
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:15,960
 at the foot of the cross.

594
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:20,240
 Thank you for saving us and changing our identity.

595
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:22,320
 And we are your children.

596
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:25,280
 We are your sons and daughters.

597
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:29,000
 And may you use us, may you continue to change us

598
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,840
 into your Son's image.

599
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:35,160
 In Christ's name we pray, amen.

600
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,160
 Well, you're dismissed.

601
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,960
 Thank you very much, and I will see you next Sunday,

602
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:41,040
 and worship God together.

603
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:51,040
 [BLANK_AUDIO]

